## `manifest.webmanifest`

```json
{
  "name": "Z Extemp Timer",
  "short_name": "Z Timer",
  "description": "Offline-capable Z Extemp Timer installable on Android and Windows.",
  "start_url": "./index.html",
  "display": "standalone",
  "background_color": "#f9fafb",
  "theme_color": "#111827",
  "icons": [
    {
      "src": "logo.png",
      "sizes": "512x512",
      "type": "image/png",
      "purpose": "any maskable"
    }
  ]
}
